This is a fork of libNova, Celestial Mechanics Library, maintained for use as a git submodule and the CMake build system. Added a branch 'stable' which is paegged to the latest tag on the original repo as of 5-2-2022 (version 0.16), so parent projects can lock to a stable version. 

Original repository; https://sourceforge.net/p/libnova/libnova

Documentation

Doxygen (http://www.doxygen.org) is needed to build documentation.
It can be generated by doing a "make doc" in doc/.
 
